QuestData.Title: Mammoth Soul
QuestData.Description: <The Mammoth Soul is brave and protective. The shape of the mammoth will be yours to call upon.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Mammoth Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Mammoth Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, the mammoth. This shape is now yours to call upon.
